summary: Prettier Aela the Huntress, in my opinion.
descriptionHtml:
Want a prettier follower, without having to add unwanted and usually broken NPCs to your game. Simple, I changed Aela\'s hair and makeup. She\'s now much easier on the eyes in my opinion.

REQUIRED MODS:
ApachiiShyHair_v_1_5_Full (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/10168)

RECOMMENDED MODS:
(Only if you want her to look exactly like mine, but these will change ALL female bodies in the game)
Calientes Female Body Mod BBE v3-2 Set to Curvy (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2666)
Envision Face for CBBE (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/7897)
Sporty Sexy Map for CBBE and the optional file Sporty Gloss for CBBE (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/13377)
Killer Keos Skimpy CBBE Armor Set V6-6-7 (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/3654)

When downloading, choose either the first download OR the Alternative download. DO NOT CHOOSE BOTH.
author: jaxxisyourfix
